import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { LoginservisService } from '../servisi/loginservis.service'; import { Ucenik } from '../models/ucenik'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register', templateUrl: './register.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register.component.css'] }) export class RegisterComponent { constructor(private servis: LoginservisService) {} user: Ucenik = new Ucenik() gradeO : Number[] = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8] gradeH : Number[] = [1,2,3,4] selectedFile: File | null = null; onFileSelected(event: any) { this.selectedFile = event.target.files[0]; } register(){ this.user.picture = this.selectedFile; const passwordRegex = /^(?=.*[A-Z])(?=.*[a-z]{3,})(?=.*\d)(?=.*[@$!%*?&])[A-Za-z\d@$!%*?&]{6,10}$/; if (!passwordRegex.test(this.user.password)) { alert('Format sifre je los ispravi'); return; } this.servis.register(this.user).subscribe( data=>{ if(data.message=="ok") alert("Dodato") } ) } } Log in
